compile & install:
  to compile this plugin, MySQL-5.5.* source is required.
  
  1. assume you want to use plugin's directory name: rpl_stat ,
     and assume you are under the same dir of this INSTALL file
  2. mkdir <mysql-src-dir/plugin/rpl_stat
  3. cp -r . <mysql-src-dir>/plugin/rpl_stat
  4. cd <mysql-src-dir>
  5. cmake source if not
  6. make
  7. cp <mysql-src-dir>/plugin/rpl_stat/rpl_stat_plugin.so to where your
     MySQL 5.5.* installation directory is

  
  